Plugin for standard SEO NAP Schema from google map and seo citation checker

== Description ==

This is a simple but effective plugin for displaying the business NAP using the google places business address.
It also displays the google reviews and suggests citations based on the country the business is located in.
This plugin help the business recognised by search engine and help to pull more website traffic.

==Plugin Features==
* Get advantage of registering on google places.
* Have the exact address of your business on your website.
* Display the correct google map based on the google places registration.
* Easier to display google user reviews anywhere on your website just using a shortcode.
* Citation checker helps you to get registered on other sites ideal for your business location like yellow pages or local business review sites like www.yelp.com

==Contents==
The WordPress Plugin Simple Local SEO includes the following files:
1) This README file.
2) A subdirectory called wp-simple-local-seo that represents the core plugin file.

== Installation ==

1) Copy the 'wp-simple-local-seo' directory into your wp-content/plugins directory
2) Navigate to the Plugins dashboard page
3) Locate the menu item that reads 'Simple Local SEO'
4) Click on Activate




